Billion Dollar Secret



Company Summary
HRG Group, Inc. is a diversified holding company. Its operations are conducted through companies which offer branded consumer products as well as life insurance and annuity products. Branded Consumer Product consists of consumer batteries, residential locksets, residential builders' hardware, faucets, shaving and grooming products, personal care products, small household appliances, specialty pet supplies, lawn, garden and home pest control products, personal insect repellents. Life insurance and annuity products include asset-backed loans and own energy assets. HRG Group, Inc., formerly known as Harbinger Group Inc., is headquartered in New York.   

















 



















HRG Group Inc (HRG)  Company Profile | Reuters.com


























































