HRG Group, Inc., incorporated on November 3, 2009, is a holding company. The Company operates through two segments: Consumer Products and Insurance. The Consumer Products segment consists of the Company's subsidiary, Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. (Spectrum Brands). The Insurance segment includes its subsidiary, Front Street Re (Delaware) Ltd. (Front Street). Through Spectrum Brands, the Company is a diversified global branded consumer products company. The Company offers seven product categories: consumer batteries, small appliances, global pet supplies, home and garden control products, personal care products, hardware and home improvement products and global auto care. Through Front Street, the Company is engaged in the business of providing long-term reinsurance, including reinsurance to the specialty insurance sector of fixed, deferred and payout annuities. The Company's subsidiary, Fidelity & Guaranty Life (FGL), provides life insurance and annuity products. FGL also sells single premium immediate annuities (SPIAs), which provide a series of periodic payments for a fixed period of time or for the life of the policyholder. The Company's subsidiaries also include FS HoldCo II Ltd., HGI Asset Management Holdings, LLC, HGI Energy Holdings, LLC and HGI Funding, LLC.Spectrum Brands manufactures, markets and/or distributes its products in approximately 160 countries in the North America (NA); Europe, Middle East and Africa (EMEA); Latin America (LATAM) and Asia-Pacific (APAC) regions through a range of trade channels, including retailers, wholesalers and distributors, original equipment manufacturers (OEMs), construction companies, and hearing aid professionals. Spectrum Brands offers five product lines: Global Batteries & Appliances (GBA); Hardware & Home Improvement (HHI); Global Pet Supplies (PET); Home and Garden (H&G), and Global Auto Care (GAC).The Company competes with Energizer Holdings, Inc., Berkshire Hathaway, Matsushita, Newell Brands, General Electric, De'Longhi America, SharkNinja, NACCO Industries, SEB S.A., Whirlpool Corporation, Conair Corporate, Koninklijke Philips N.V., Glen Dimplex, The Procter & Gamble Company, Wahl Clipper Corporation, Helen of Troy Limited, Allegion, The Hillman Group, Hampton Hardware, Crown Bolt, Kohler, Masco, Fortune Brands, American Standard, Glacier Bay, AquaSource, Mars Corporation, The Hartz Mountain Corporation, Central Garden & Pet Company, The Scotts Miracle-Gro Company, Bayer A.G., S.C. Johnson & Son, Inc., Henkel AG & Co. KGaA, Valvoline, Prestone, Turtle Wax, Black Magic, Mothers, Meguiars, Lucas, Sea Foam, Athene Life Re Ltd., Global Atlantic Financial Group Limited, Guggenheim Life and Annuity Company, Reinsurance Group of America, Incorporated, Legal & General Reinsurance Company Ltd. and Resolution Life Holdings, Inc.

» Full Overview of HRG







